          <figure class="my-10">
            <LazyImage src="/images/trailhead-mobile-surveillance-trailer.webp"
              alt="A solar-powered mobile surveillance trailer with extended camera mast parked at the edge of a Pacific Northwest forest trailhead parking lot in late-afternoon light"
